title: The Last Days Of Jim Morrison [French - Needs Eng Subs]
description:
The Last Days Of Jim Morrison

French TV Documentary 
Broadcast on November 30, 2006

One hour investigation into Jim Morrison&#039;s mysterious death on July 3, 1971 in Paris. Features interviews with Doors drummer John Densmore, Doors manager Bill Siddons, Pamela Courson&#039;s mother, Jim&#039;s best friend Frank Lisciandro, the fireman who responded to the emergency call and discovered his body, Herve Muller (Jim&#039;s friend while he was in Paris), and others. 

A great documentary, but unfortunately (for non-French speaking people) it&#039;s completely in French. This needs English subtitles! 

Any French-speaking viewers care to give it a shot and translate it for us American Doors fans?
